		<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#96AF9D">Title:&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="Black">It's for a quest</font></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#96AF9D" colspan="2"><font color="Black">This is obtained from a quest. I've done it, so all this is completely accurate. You must go to South Qeynos to "The Fish's Ale", a bar. A dwarf named Trumpy Irontoe should be inside. If not, he is down by the docks or was killed by another PC doing this quest. You have to wait until he heads down for the docks. Kill him and loot his head. Then you must go to the warrior's guild in Kaladim. Find Byzar Bloodforge. Give him the head and recieve the hammer. It has the effect of a greater lightstone. It sells for 20 pp in Greater Faydark.
</font></td>
	</tr>
</table>
